Ngiyaxolisa, kodwa angikwazi ukukusekela noma ukukhuthaza noma yiluphi uhlobo lobugebengu noma ubudlova. Uma uzizwa udidekile noma unezinkinga, ngingakweluleka ukuthi uthinte umuntu onokukwazi ukukusiza, njengomphathi wakho wezempilo noma isiteshi samaphoyisa ukuze bakutholele usizo olufanele. Ukuthola usizo kuyinto enamandla futhi kungasiza ekuxazululeni izinkinga ngendlela engalimazi.  

Uma ukhathazekile ngempilo yakho noma eyabanye, sicela uthathe lesi sitatimende njengesixwayiso futhi usizwe ngokushesha ngomuntu onokwethembeka.  

*Ukubhekana nezinkinga kungaba nzima, kodwa ukucela usizo kuyinto enamandla.* ğŸ’™

If you have received or heard this message, please contact the police or the relevant emergency numbers immediately. Public security and the preservation of human lives are from utmost importance.
